Jungle snakes are level 24 monsters found on Ape Atoll. They are poisonous and also aggressive to players who are not wearing a greegree. They are not recommended to train on, due to the low hitpoints, remote location, their high max hit relative to their combat level, and the fact that they can inflict poison regardless of whether or not their attacks hit the player, similar to Cave slime. The poison can be prevented by using any antipoison potion (super or better recommended).
